snippet.title: MSX Turbo R Game: Illusion City (1991 Micro Cabin)
snippet.description:
This is a cyberpunk RPG set in Hong Kong after the year 2000. As far as I can understand, Hong Kong suffered a disastrous biological accident, leaving the city in ruins and creating many mutants.

Please like this video and subscribe to my channel for more great retro content.

#RetroGames #RetroGaming #OldGames #ClassicGames
